285
00:20:46,630 --> 00:20:47,660
Attention!

286
00:21:01,150 --> 00:21:03,240
Brigade Commander of the Defending Guards,

287
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:05,160
I, Liang Xiang of the Imperial Guards,

