295
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:36,110
I sincerely hope

296
00:21:36,830 --> 00:21:38,430
you will treat it seriously.

297
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:40,760
Mr. Liang, please rest assured!

298
00:21:40,850 --> 00:21:42,600
I will take this responsibility seriously

299
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:45,360
to keep the capital
and His Majesty safe and sound.

300
00:21:45,360 --> 00:21:47,690
I wish you, Mr. Liang, to take care as well.

301
00:21:48,900 --> 00:21:51,310
Thank you, Brigade Commander.

302
00:21:53,360 --> 00:21:54,080
Tufang.

303
00:21:55,050 --> 00:21:57,450
no need for formalities between us, right?

304
00:21:57,620 --> 00:21:59,160
I've booked a table at Taifeng Restaurant

305
00:21:59,160 --> 00:22:00,200
tonight.

306
00:22:00,820 --> 00:22:02,150
Join me for a few drinks.

307
