00:23:21,830 --> 00:23:23,920
Look back at the Wu, Yue,
Qi, Qin, and Chu dynasties;

315
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:26,750
in the blink of an eye, it moved on
to the Liang, Tang, Jin, Han, and Zhou.

316
00:23:26,750 --> 00:23:29,480
Bravo!

317
00:23:29,590 --> 00:23:31,440
Today, I'll tell a story about Wu Song,

318
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:33,110
the second eldest in the Wu family.

319
00:23:33,110 --> 00:23:34,510
Good evening, officers.

320
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:35,920
My surname is Li.

321
00:23:35,940 --> 00:23:37,420
I booked a table here earlier.

322
00:23:37,420 --> 00:23:38,860
Commander Li of the Defending Guards?

323
00:23:38,860 --> 00:23:39,730
Yes.

324
00:23:40,170 --> 00:23:41,970
Please follow me, Commander Li.

325
00:23:42,590 --> 00:23:44,720
Another officer has already arrived.

326
00:23:44,850 --> 00:23:46,330
His brother's called Wu Tianling.

327
00:23:46,330 --> 00:23:47,200
And he's called

328
00:23:47,680 --> 00:23:48,440
Wu Tiangang.

329
00:23:49,510 --> 00:23:51,750
His elder brother was
all about literature and books,

330
00:23:51,750 --> 00:23:53,190
yet Wu Song loved martial arts.

331
00:23:53,190 --> 00:23:55,890
Wu Song often trained with swords
and spears in the back garden.

332
00:23:55,890 --> 00:23:57,880
And he also learned boxing
in the Shaolin Temple.

333
00:23:57,880 --> 00:24:00,270
Only after practicing kung fu
for over eight years

334
00:24:00,270 --> 00:24:01,830
did he start to learn
the Eagle Claw technique.

335
00:24:01,830 --> 00:24:03,550
On the wall, he practiced
the Iron Palm technique,

336
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:05,200
Power-suction technique,
and Pristine Qigong.

337
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:07,510
With stronger skills than others,
he had defeated

338
00:24:07,510 --> 00:24:09,970
everyone in the Shaolin Temple
three times.

339
00:24:32,820 --> 00:24:35,150
Rumors are spread in Beijing, saying that

340
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:38,820
I, Liang Xiang, sent someone
to kill Kaizhi.

341
00:24:40,790 --> 00:24:41,790
Do you believe it?

342
00:24:52,510 --> 00:24:53,960
No, of course.

343
00:24:55,900 --> 00:24:56,660
Why?

344
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:02,080
The night he was assassinated,

345
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:05,010
I had a talk with him.

346
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:07,720
The gun went off

347
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:09,180
when I was just

348
00:25:10,930 --> 00:25:11,930
leaving Zhentou.

349
00:25:16,550 --> 00:25:17,550
So,

350
00:25:19,550 --> 00:25:21,200
you were near the scene?

351
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:26,340
You could say that.

352
00:25:35,990 --> 00:25:37,640
Don't look at me like that.

353
00:25:38,850 --> 00:25:41,150
I, Li Renjun, have got nothing
to feel guilty about.

354
00:25:41,150 --> 00:25:43,150
I didn't stop trying to hold him back

355
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:45,250
until the very last minute.

