00:27:18,110 --> 00:27:19,100
Qianli,

384
00:27:21,510 --> 00:27:23,070
how come you seem like

385
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:27,170
a different person all of a sudden?

386
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:36,570
No longer naive and simple, right?

387
00:27:36,720 --> 00:27:37,370
No,

388
00:27:41,260 --> 00:27:43,520
you've become even more sophisticated.

389
00:27:51,750 --> 00:27:53,510
Let's cut to the chase, Tufang.

390
00:27:54,910 --> 00:27:56,070
It's not necessary for us

391
00:27:56,070 --> 00:27:57,870
