00:31:12,430 --> 00:31:13,420
Your sister is back too.

442
00:31:13,420 --> 00:31:14,150
Where is she?

443
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:14,960
She's at home.

444
00:31:15,070 --> 00:31:16,750
I'm here for a meeting
at the Ministry of Education.

