519
00:34:16,210 --> 00:34:18,290
Get me the Belgian Consul on the line.

520
00:34:18,850 --> 00:34:20,310
Alright, I'll be waiting.

521
00:34:21,210 --> 00:34:22,520
The Belgian Consul?

522
00:34:25,750 --> 00:34:27,420
